g.text: All dates are in DD/MM/YYYY. Chart made by Connor (Dizgovzy), last updated 19/09/2023.
Commissioner known as Deputy Commissioner during Naifon's Term.

Gor Kebab lost elector status (ejected from WA for multying) on 02/01/2020. At the time, it was believed that this was due to Gor Kebab's fiancee using the same internet network as Gor Kebab. Runner-up Rivierenland appointed.
Rivierenland lost elector status (moved regions, to Thaecia) on 26/01/2020.
Wombelland appointed for being most endorsed non-government elector on 26/01/2020

Gor Kebab appointed via the Commissions (Elections) Act 2020 on 24/02/2020, through the puppet Gor Nacho. It was revealed in 2023 by self-admission that Gor Kebab had been WA Multying, and thus arguably should not have been reinstated.
Eurasies CTEd on 20/12/2020, position vacant until runner-up Eritei appointed on 22/12/2020.
Einswenn lost elector status (moved regions, to Forest) on 11/02/2021. Runner-up Republic of Satherland appointed.

Rivierenland lost elector status (resigned from WA) and was given 24 hours to rejoin. GanymedEuropa was then offered the position but did not respond. Walfo was then offered the position and accepted. 1DC vacant from 11/10/2021 to 14/10/2021.
